name: Calgary Weddings
overview: My name is Bob Turner. I was born the 2nd of December in Fernie, BC Canada. Growing up in Canada I was close to the mountains so I used to ski a lot in the winter and mountain bike too in the summer. In the nineties snowboarding became popular and I quickly became passionate for the sport. Soon after I started competing in half-pipe competitions with good results to boast, finishing first in several Canadian and USA-Based events. Currently IÂ´m a semi-pro snowboarder, working part time at a local heli ski mountain resort. Online I’d like to make new friends from all over the world!
